124951,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T01:24:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講下原因引發討論都好啲呀 <br />\n得個戲名好難搞喎</blockquote><br />\n唔係未睇過呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔係咁蠢啊嘛...就咁擺低片名又唔講下套野點樣發人深省,咁有咩意義?<br />\n做壞個頭,後面個班都只係擺個片名出黎就算,成個post得一個會講下點樣套戲點樣發人深省<br />\n綠里奇蹟係點樣發人深省法都要講下先得架...因為好人無好報,做咁多好事最後都要坐電椅?定係其他原因?"},{"pid":"0459a3542d31e4b982a31cdaf7d53a8a1897f9d3","tid":499251,"uid":136662,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T01:36:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講下原因引發討論都好啲呀 <br />\n得個戲名好難搞喎</blockquote><br />\n唔係未睇過呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔係咁蠢啊嘛...就咁擺低片名又唔講下套野點樣發人深省,咁有咩意義?<br />\n做壞個頭,後面個班都只係擺個片名出黎就算,成個post得一個會講下點樣套戲點樣發人深省<br />\n綠里奇蹟係點樣發人深省法都要講下先得架...因為好人無好報,做咁多好事最後都要坐電椅?定係其他原因?</blockquote><br />\n咁就更加唔好講原因<br />\n呢d要自己睇感受完先明<br />\n一早講晒邊個位係咁咁咁而唔係諗返轉頭原來係咁<br />\n個感覺唔同d"},{"pid":"b99609da9b08cdd921e8c8005717112d3f63cbf9","tid":499251,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T01:37:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>例牌答案 Click</blockquote><br />\n小學雞三寶"},{"pid":"790dfbed9903c191ba81805f2a01db0e035caea8","tid":499251,"uid":48276,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T01:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://reasonformovie.files.wordpress.com/2015/03/bucket-list.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Freasonformovie.files.wordpress.com%2F2015%2F03%2Fbucket-list.jpg&h=ef2db6f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一定推呢套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aeb96e25e044edd01849c4fec33c99758f3abea","tid":499251,"uid":124951,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T01:52:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講下原因引發討論都好啲呀 <br />\n得個戲名好難搞喎</blockquote><br />\n唔係未睇過呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔係咁蠢啊嘛...就咁擺低片名又唔講下套野點樣發人深省,咁有咩意義?<br />\n做壞個頭,後面個班都只係擺個片名出黎就算,成個post得一個會講下點樣套戲點樣發人深省<br />\n綠里奇蹟係點樣發人深省法都要講下先得架...因為好人無好報,做咁多好事最後都要坐電椅?定係其他原因?</blockquote><br />\n咁就更加唔好講原因<br />\n呢d要自己睇感受完先明<br />\n一早講晒邊個位係咁咁咁而唔係諗返轉頭原來係咁<br />\n個感覺唔同d</blockquote><br />\n''你鍾意邊套戲啊??''<br />\n''綠里奇蹟,原因唔講,呢d要自己睇感受完先明!!''<br />\n''......''<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔講既個post唔好叫''推薦''啦,撻個戲名出黎就算"},{"pid":"423281702881171daeb55232b6746effd8594b9c","tid":499251,"uid":42820,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:05:12.000Z","msg":"喜瑪拉雅星<br />\n六樓後座"},{"pid":"fc7a90d0b462c47827694f693e8819900d1e2054","tid":499251,"uid":43141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:11:32.000Z","msg":"silence"},{"pid":"7352680f1f32681fe8c878337b0b4b14a7a4bf3e","tid":499251,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:15:18.000Z","msg":"The scent of women <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4916a99a6c149c6fa196c2165362cfe6e24787fd","tid":499251,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:15:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Scent of women <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}